    "The insights we learned from training these models highlight the importance of rigorous data processing and the potential of data synthesis in developing capable AI agents.",
    "By releasing the xLAM series, we aim to democratize access to high-performance models for agent tasks, thereby accelerating progress in the field.",
    "Our data synthesis pipeline relies on large LLMs such as DeepSeek-V2 and Mixtral-8x22b-Inst.",
    "This dependence may result in extended data generation times when utilizing less powerful GPUs.",
    "Future work will focus on developing more efficient pipelines capable of operating effectively with both smaller and larger LLMs."
